listings.comment: One of the best sellers I have worked with. Designed my best website to this date. And worked on any changes consistently after job was done A+++++++

Shofiqul was easy to get a hold of whenever we needed him he responded in a timely manner. He went above and beyond whenever we needed help with anything. He is friendly, creative, polite, easy to work with and we would definitely recommend him to anyone who wants a great quality website! We will continue to use him for future projects!

The final product fell short of my expectations with noticeable attention to details. While working together was average, there was a clear need for more effort and proactiveness, leaving me feeling the value received was quite low.
It took a year to get simple little details correct and my work is still yet to be completed but yet he closed the order.

I had the pleasure of working with Shofiqul on my website, and I couldn’t be more satisfied with the experience. He was incredibly patient, attentive, and professional throughout the entire process. Every request I made was executed flawlessly, and he went above and beyond to ensure that the final result met my expectations.

His expertise and dedication truly set him apart. Whether it was design adjustments, functionality improvements, or technical tweaks, he handled everything with precision and efficiency. If you’re looking for a reliable and skilled web developer, I highly recommend Shofiqul! I will definitely work with him again in the future.
